title: What Would You Do? Lunchbox Has An Incident at A Restaurant + What Do You Hate / Love on The Show? Update in Sam Hunt Divorce (Wednesday Part 2)
itunes:title: What Would You Do? Lunchbox Has An Incident at A Restaurant + What Do You Hate / Love on The Show? Update in Sam Hunt Divorce (Wednesday Part 2)
description:
Lunchbox was out at a restaurant when his food was given to another table…and then brought over to his table after being set down in front of them. What would you do in this situation?? Bobby takes callers trying to find what listeners love and hate about the show. Bobby shares an update about the news that came out yesterday about Sam Hunt.
